{
  "name": "_example_responses_passthrough_streaming",
  "description": "ResponsesPassthroughAdapter 字节级透传 SSE 验证 —— 自定义第三方 provider apiFormat=responses + 入站 /v1/responses → upstream OpenAI Responses API SSE 原样返。前缀 _ 不进 list_fixtures()。",
  "provider": "custom-third-party",
  "client_request": {
    "method": "POST",
    "path": "/v1/responses",
    "headers": {
      "content-type": "application/json",
      "authorization": "<redacted>"
    },
    "body_json": {
      "model": "gpt-5",
      "stream": true,
      "input": [
        { "role": "user", "content": [{"type": "input_text", "text": "hi"}] }
      ]
    }
  },
  "upstream": [
    {
      "url_pattern": "https://api\\.openai\\.com/v1/responses",
      "method": "POST",
      "response": {
        "status": 200,
        "headers": {
          "content-type": "text/event-stream"
        },
        "stream": [
          { "data": "event: response.created\ndata: {\"sequence_number\":0,\"type\":\"response.created\",\"response\":{\"id\":\"resp_passthrough_test\",\"object\":\"response\",\"status\":\"in_progress\",\"model\":\"gpt-5\"}}\n\n" },
          { "data": "event: response.output_text.delta\ndata: {\"sequence_number\":1,\"type\":\"response.output_text.delta\",\"delta\":\"hi\"}\n\n" },
          { "data": "event: response.completed\ndata: {\"sequence_number\":2,\"type\":\"response.completed\",\"response\":{\"id\":\"resp_passthrough_test\",\"object\":\"response\",\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n\n" }
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "expected": {
    "status": 200,
    "headers_contain": {
      "content-type": "text/event-stream"
    },
    "stream_substrings": [
      "resp_passthrough_test",
      "response.output_text.delta",
      "\"delta\":\"hi\"",
      "response.completed",
      "\"sequence_number\":0",
      "\"sequence_number\":1",
      "\"sequence_number\":2"
    ]
  },
  "notes": "关键证明:① 上游 sequence_number / event 类型字面值字节级穿透代理(没被 ChatToResponsesConverter 重写);② 上游 resp_id 直接保留(没被 chatcmpl→resp_ 重写);③ Responses API envelope 由上游产生,代理不参与构造。等价于 OpenAiChatAdapter 的 byte-level passthrough 行为,但适用 apiFormat=responses + /responses 入站路径。"
}
